snippet: The agricultural equipment maker said shipping hurt its performance in the most recent quarter.
abstract: Deere & Co says shipping hurt its performance in the fiscal third quarter; net income was $788 million, or $1.98 a share, up 11 percent from $712.3 million, or $1.69 a share, in the year-ago quarter; revenue rose 15 percent to $9.59 billion.
lead_paragraph: The agricultural equipment maker said shipping hurt its performance in the most recent quarter.

headline.main: Deere, Falling Short on Profit, Partly Faults Production Delays
headline.print_headline: Deere, Falling Short on Profit, Partly Faults Production Delays
